Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(50,50)\a6)}[Gloster:发音同Gloucester]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gloster?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是应该在塞尔旺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是体形大一点的KnightMare罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点投降不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  只用一台机体就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18区的势力终于肃清了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于今后的行动计划
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  让你们陪我处理愚弟的身后事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说公主所在的地方就是我们的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对待11区可不能这么直截了当
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会把你逼出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛维斯的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}皇女和魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:03:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你那个样子  好像已经在外面吃过饭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心你是不是被卷入那个叫ZERO的人惹出的混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的电话也打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  难得C.C.来做客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一个奇特的朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然只有名字的缩写
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是  哥哥的恋人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他是约定了将来的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来是指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  那个  她是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  哥哥你意外地动作很快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人各有志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会觉得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你在干什么啊  C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄湿了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来  要赶快去盥洗室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你准备换洗衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉  我会马上来收拾的  不要乱动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  刚才那是骗人的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的  开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了嘛  C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是指那个  你应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你中意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赐给你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这让我的行程大幅前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行程?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏布里塔尼亚的预定表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来认为开始行动还要很久才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为你能破坏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用那个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有这个力量  我也打算做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我预料的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎是个有趣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接下来打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在被军队追吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是军队  但只是其中一部分而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要稍微躲一下就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在这里忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你打算待在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人给我睡地板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果被抓了你也会很困扰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果露宿的话会被送去辅导
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管你的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我的立场就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌缠人的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个没有紧张感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  你怎么得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你那时说的契约…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福岛  高知  广岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是第七件了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自ZERO出现以来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自ZERO之后  其他的团体也在努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚代理执政官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那次的ORANGE事件而失去了洞察力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本来就不是那块料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此军队和警察的配合也变得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:05:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给我们带来了很多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我们吧  藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为ZERO  布里塔尼亚变得混乱起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是我们日本解放战线重新站起来的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都传来把红莲二式交给ZERO的消息还是不确定情报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太执著于ZERO的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被人抓住把柄的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ORANGE到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs22}{\fad(100,100)\pos(222,195)}朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你的问题你一概不回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却反过来问我问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想回答的话不回答不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ORANGE什么的  是捏造的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那些互称同志的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却只因一个疑点就轻易分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[注：此处报刊的英文及中文翻译见附件]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界都在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界因为你而变动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是想看到这种情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这种混乱只不过是手段之一而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界要接受更大混乱的冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀一等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第11方面军从属14107号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于杀害克洛维斯殿下的嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于证据不足而被释放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  突然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我没想到下面会有人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  我也没想到上面会有女孩子掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我被坏人追
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  你能救救我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅殿下的就任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被那个ORANGE事件影响
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去  我们纯血派的忠诚会被怀疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚卿受了贿赂这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么ORANGE是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  杰雷米亚卿背后在做些什么是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说自己什么都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种和巴托雷一样的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚卿的记忆也混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新宿被夺走Sutherland时我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是名人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木玄武首相的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀一等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被坏人追什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵  喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤了吗喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵  喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了一步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他等等我们就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的被释放了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据不足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他也因为ZERO的事被好好调查了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  为什么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总是我单恋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会单恋的人是很善良的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才为什么撒那种谎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在意我的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?  啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再陪陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得和在布里塔尼亚的时候没什么不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲是从本国来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到上周为止还是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说到上周为止还是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生是指高中生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要观光的话什么时候都可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题连发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我不是责怪你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  因为今天是最后的休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想要出来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看11区
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底是怎么样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  不用找我也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我很高兴是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能再带我去一个地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请吩咐  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去新宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我看看新宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于上次的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  就是在浴室那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能查一下对方的号码
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和那边联系一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个电话是学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会以这种样子回本国
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和那个女人扯上关系就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要到处乱走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧  反正是在学校内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那么死板嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里可是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪里都是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她今天也在做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对她用了Geass  让她每天来这里做记号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geass?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指这个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在缔结契约的时候我是这么听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于持续时间的实验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总要理解武器的性能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你太任性的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个会对我有效果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你是共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会做出对我们不利的事来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新宿贫民区已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得人们刚刚开始回到这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对着11区果然还是不想用我的RG啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这边  对人炮弹的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那里拍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗  关于ZERO的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是丘威尔卿那里来的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对新宿第四空域发动非常战斗命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[大公：对君主一族男子的尊称]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  大公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘威尔卿  接下来就拜托你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是想和杰雷米亚卿联系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看样子现在不是说这个的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚的猪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是11区人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我们11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们输给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战败国的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些布里塔尼亚的混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  是枢木朱雀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉克洛维斯的枢木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  是ZERO干掉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙只不过是奴隶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么名誉布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己还觉得很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊严  朋友  灵魂都出卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还算是日本人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这条布里塔尼亚的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是受过训练的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再对同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的PrimeG和MX4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明明还是名誉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么让他们逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们干掉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你早就杀了很多11区人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁还会认为你是好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不允许你再侮辱这个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用Geass需要直接看到对方的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜这种程度的透明度没有影响
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效距离大约是270米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  被施予Geass的前后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是中途
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有记忆上的丢失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可以认为是Geass介入大脑所造成的损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设这是光学情报的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反射也是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你在那么短的时间内调查了那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:16:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是控制了世界三分之一以上的帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有所谓的谨慎过度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11区人姑且不论
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是布里塔尼亚人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用Geass来作战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手未免也太强大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要强大就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱小是不对的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在只有10岁的我们看来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界非常的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饥饿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贪污  腐败
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争以及恐怖主义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复不断的憎恨连锁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的斗争游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要有谁来打断这个连锁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太理想了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我没有想过能让这些东西全部消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有傲慢到那个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够不失去重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最起码  有一个没有战争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那种顺心的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要某个人胜利了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争就能结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果放弃了追求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲就白白牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木首相的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那场战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲不得不死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让杀害克洛维斯殿下的犯人逃掉的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就在这里算算清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙的丘威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说发现了ZERO是假的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在科奈莉娅殿下到达上任前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要先把内部清理干净
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚  这是肃清
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞希尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很危险  快上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯血派的内斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被释放了  可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要让你陪我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是拿到Lancelot战斗资料的好机会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就在这里告别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能不去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是Lancelot的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和四个人做对手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要激动  杰雷米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会把你当成战死处理的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会影响你家族的名声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  想要把我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  ORANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到底为了什么而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了皇室的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚的威光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同为布里塔尼亚军的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是  名誉布里塔尼亚人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向导兵器  Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别派遣想要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁  只要介入一律杀无赦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能眼睁睁地看着无意义的战斗发生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[MVS：Maser Vibration Sword的缩写，镭射振动剑]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MVS?  已经被实用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到这个地步也不能退缩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴之间为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来救我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么至少也要干掉ORANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚卿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[维蕾塔·纽 Villetta Nu,纯血派战士]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蕾塔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还想继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都退下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于能理解了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要使用CHAOS炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:19:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个名誉布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单手就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三方  都请收起手中的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我之名下令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难  难道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是布里塔尼亚第三公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[Euphemia Li Britannia]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲米娅·Li·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这里的指挥权交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都退下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是…公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗  罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不常在公众面前出现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实…实在是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我并不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚才太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同你失去了父亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也失去了兄长克洛维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否为了创造不再失去重要的人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而助我一臂之力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  深感荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了  由菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉皇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种场合请叫我总督
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲米娅副总督
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为我们是亲姐妹所以更要遵守这些规定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你那边的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我们已经准备了盛大的宴会欢迎皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:22:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松懈了  愚蠢了  堕落了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住帝国居民的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是从今天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转入这所阿修佛德学园的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对莎莉和利瓦尔他们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连对朱雀和娜娜莉也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已经没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:23:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.96,0:24:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果C.C.说她是我的共犯的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也只有做了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想对自己撒谎了
